        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fair Accounting for Condominium Construction Act </b></p> <p>This bill exempts certain residential construction contracts from the requirement to use the percentage of completion method of accounting. The<em> percentage of completion method</em> is a tax accounting method in which the revenues and expenses of long-term contracts are recognized as a percentage of the work completed in a particular period.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
